            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> parboiled chips </strong>to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until crispy and golden – these are your<strong> twice cooked chips</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
