    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice the <strong>remaining orange</strong>, then cut each slice in half</p><p>Tip: Use a sharp knife to get rid of any pith!</p><p>Cut the<strong> gem lettuce</strong> into 8 <span class=\"text-danger\">[16] </span>thin wedges, give them a wash and pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
